{
  "stem": "1530.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 22.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we told our whole story to the attache.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he almost cried.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he says, I never had such an experience.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right away he gave us chocolate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says, I don't have [? wax ?] clothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I have little soldiers clothing, and I want you to get in it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, you know, this was in [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oelsk, ?] or was this in Odessa already even?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, the point is, I think that we got with the train to Odessa, and this happened in Odessa.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah, it was very cute.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very proud of it, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And wonderful food, and-- anyway, I think this was already at Odessa, where the American Army attache.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said to us, now you say you're Americans, but we don't really know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I believe you three orphans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm going to investigate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I guess he got in touch with the FBI.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they got, right away, touch with my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they knew that we were alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said-- he said, I tell you what I'm going to do for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There are 30 Liberty ships in Odessa here, which brought armaments to Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- I'm going to try to get on one of those ships, even you have no papers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The three girls.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went next day, and none of the Liberty ships want to take women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said to them, if you don't think them, the other one will take them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he got us on a Liberty ship, which was a convoy of 30 ships.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the war was still going on at January--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--something, January '45.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- oh, but by this time it's not January.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we went-- we were with the Russians for six weeks.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
